Changelog for Pic.

Pic 1.1.1-pl (January 30, 2015)
====================================
 - Add check if cached file changed

Pic 1.1.0-beta1 (October 09, 2014)
====================================
 - Add transparent color (bgcolor=`transparent`)
 - Add image resize with max field (mode=`maxField`)
 - Add hex mode (mode=`hexagon`)

Pic 1.0.0-beta1 (April 09, 2014)
====================================
 - New build script
 - Add image resize with side fields

Pic 0.3.0-beta1 (May 14, 2013)
====================================
 - Fully covered with unit tests.
 - Fixed bug with too big images.
 - Optimized code.

Pic 0.2.1-pl1 (March 22, 2013)
====================================
 - Initial release.